{"tid":2006162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律政司就《禁蒙面法》部分違憲裁決向終審法院申上訴許可 泛民議員亦提出上訴","createTime":"2020-05-07T14:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T18:41:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6f4b0c2154a47abf9f18d8e8074134e77eac27","tid":2006162,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"上訴庭早前推翻高等法院原訟庭裁決，裁定政府引用《緊急法》訂立規例屬合憲，以及《禁蒙面法》部分合憲。律政司今（7日）表示，已就裁決提出申請許可，以向終審法院提出上訴。至於提出司法覆核的24名泛民立法會議員，同樣已就裁決提出上訴。律政司表示，由於司法程序仍未完畢，目前不適宜評論。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭早前頒下判辭，裁定立法會與回歸前的立法局一樣，當中包括賦予行政機關訂立附屬法例的權力，法庭亦可從中審視有關法例是否合憲，認為《基本法》本身已容許行政機關訂立緊急情况附屬法例，裁定《緊急法》合憲。<br />\n<br />\n至於《禁蒙面法》，上訴庭認為，很多大規模遊行和示威往往演變成暴動，當中大部分暴徒以全黑裝束以逃避犯罪行為責任，可見未經批准集結變化無常，故警方需阻遏人們通過佩戴蒙面物品，以妨礙《公安條例》條文正當執行，故裁定《禁蒙面法》在非法集結和未經批准集結的情況下屬合憲。但上訴庭認為，警方已有足夠警權規管合法集結，加上佩戴蒙面物品的行為本身並非刑事罪行，故裁定條例在公眾集會及遊行中屬違憲。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 明報"},{"pid":"e005b421655195cadd9f16664e2698c5e8f065c4","tid":2006162,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"法治已死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24491ff5ca3904e3ddb26dd70fcccd182986607a","tid":2006162,"uid":65449,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"社會上有風氣二次創作支那歌 咁呀？國歌法囉<br />\n好多人遮樣睇唔到拉唔到人 咁呀？ 禁蒙面法囉 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affa3eda9086b89306e8aa5084066db720dc83f1","tid":2006162,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"馬道立會點？公正？歸邊？"},{"pid":"f13a3f3521f229aa3cd34d7fca5e0d38bd1375c9","tid":2006162,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qENmYPF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqENmYPF.jpg&h=18cf5c1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咬定青山不放鬆 <br />\n立根原在破岩中。<br />\n千磨萬擊還堅勁 <br />\n任爾東西南北風。<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"afd4981fc4aaa81dc72a40000918044b2a716e39","tid":2006162,"uid":225130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"affa3eda9086b89306e8aa5084066db720dc83f1","tid":2006162,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"馬道立會點？公正？歸邊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"中嬸點奶都唔會紅得過上訴庭<br />\n所以一係維持原判 一係比依家既結果好"},{"pid":"567d20f5522b9ba27fd2a943ec9fb6ecde0b6b86","tid":2006162,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1cc1905dfc0f45c85faf2eda128dad1c97f5fa","tid":2006162,"uid":8014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:06:06.000Z","msg":"肯定拖到張舉撚上任先判"},{"pid":"dc4dad5d53d178da6ed01a6daafbdbc1b35e1de8","tid":2006162,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"affa3eda9086b89306e8aa5084066db720dc83f1","tid":2006162,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"馬道立會點？公正？歸邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"退休先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d6a55045950a6334439e658a01a2e5aa722fba","tid":2006162,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afd4981fc4aaa81dc72a40000918044b2a716e39","tid":2006162,"uid":225130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"affa3eda9086b89306e8aa5084066db720dc83f1","tid":2006162,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:00:40.00